trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of static <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"></xref> objects, which is used when the connections are declared in content pages and the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"></xref> control is declared in a master page.
trans-unit.target: Contém uma coleção de estático <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"> </xref> objetos, que é usado quando as conexões são declaradas em páginas de conteúdo e o <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"> </xref> controle declarado em uma página mestra.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection class is used in a specific development scenario.
trans-unit.target: A classe ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection é usada em um cenário de desenvolvimento específico.

trans-unit.source: If a Web Parts application uses master pages, with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control declared in a master page, and individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> objects declared in content pages as static connections, the ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection class is used.
trans-unit.target: Se um aplicativo Web Parts usa páginas mestras, com o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>controle declarado em uma página mestra e individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>objetos declarado em páginas de conteúdo como conexões estáticas, a classe ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection é usada.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: In the content pages, multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> controls can be declared, which differs from the ordinary rule that only one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control can be declared on a page.
trans-unit.target: Nas páginas de conteúdo, vários <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>controles podem ser declarados, que difere da regra comum que apenas um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>controle pode ser declarado em uma página.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control on a content page can contain a `<StaticConnections>` element, and this element can contain one or more declared `<asp:webpartconnection>` elements.
trans-unit.target: Cada <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>controle em uma página de conteúdo pode conter um `<StaticConnections>` e esse elemento podem conter um ou mais declarado `<asp:webpartconnection>` elementos.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection class is used by the Web Parts control set to create a collection of all the static connections declared in each content page, and these collections are ultimately added to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A> collection in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control.
trans-unit.target: A classe ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection é usada pelo controle Web Parts definido para criar uma coleção de todas as conexões estáticas declarado em cada página de conteúdo, e essas coleções, por fim, são adicionadas para o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>coleção no <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>controle.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>

trans-unit.source: The ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection class is used to create the collection of static <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> objects that is referenced by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: A classe ProxyWebPartConnectionCollection é usada para criar a coleção de estático <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>objetos que é referenciado pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>do controle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager.StaticConnections%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>
